SHORT="Utility to format and create bootable USB flash drives"
cat << "EOF"
Rufus is a utility that helps format and create bootable USB flash drives,
such as USB keys/pendrives, memory sticks, etc.

It can create bootable media from:
- ISO images
- Disk images
- Executable files
- Windows installations

Rufus is particularly useful for creating UEFI bootable USB media and
supports a variety of file systems and boot options.
EOF
